INSERT INTO public.devotional (id, slug, title, author, body_md, audio_asset, date, lang, view_count, created_at, updated_at, speaker_id, video_asset, content_type) VALUES (1, 'gods-unfailing-love', 'God''s Unfailing Love', 'Ellen G. White', '# God''s Unfailing Love

"For God so loved the world that He gave His only begotten Son, that whoever believes in Him should not perish but have everlasting life." - John 3:16

## Reflection

God''s love is beyond human comprehension. It is not based on our worthiness but on His character. Today, pause and consider the depth of God''s love for you personally.

## Prayer

Dear Father, thank You for Your unconditional love. Help me to share this love with others today. Amen.', NULL, '2025-12-01', 'en', 541, '2025-12-01 16:52:31.316006+00', '2025-12-01 16:52:31.331855+00', NULL, NULL, 'text');
INSERT INTO public.devotional (id, slug, title, author, body_md, audio_asset, date, lang, view_count, created_at, updated_at, speaker_id, video_asset, content_type) VALUES (2, 'walking-in-faith', 'Walking in Faith', 'Morris Venden', '# Walking in Faith

"Now faith is the substance of things hoped for, the evidence of things not seen." - Hebrews 11:1

## Reflection

Faith is not blind belief but trust in God based on His proven character and promises. When we walk by faith, we demonstrate our confidence in God''s wisdom and timing.

## Prayer

Lord, increase my faith. Help me to trust You even when I cannot see the way forward. Amen.', NULL, '2025-11-30', 'en', 126, '2025-12-01 16:52:31.316006+00', '2025-12-01 16:52:31.331855+00', NULL, NULL, 'text');
INSERT INTO public.devotional (id, slug, title, author, body_md, audio_asset, date, lang, view_count, created_at, updated_at, speaker_id, video_asset, content_type) VALUES (3, 'the-joy-of-salvation', 'The Joy of Salvation', 'Mark Finley', '# The Joy of Salvation

"Restore to me the joy of Your salvation, and uphold me by Your generous Spirit." - Psalm 51:12

## Reflection

Salvation is not just a future hope but a present reality that brings joy and transformation. Let us rejoice in what Christ has done for us.

## Prayer

Thank You, Jesus, for the gift of salvation. Fill my heart with joy as I serve You today. Amen.', NULL, '2025-11-29', 'en', 425, '2025-12-01 16:52:31.316006+00', '2025-12-01 16:52:31.331855+00', NULL, NULL, 'text');


